  <bodyText><![CDATA[<div class="white_box_shadow"><img src="/media/13083190/ii_tours_desenzano_del_garda-for-web.jpg" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/7db02a04429d40748d8db1e25bfee948" /><br />
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><br /><strong>Special booking offers for Italy</strong></h2>
<p>Make Italy your number one holiday destination for summer 2020. A great place to spend time doing the things you love. Get your boots on and take on the many hiking trails, have your camera ready to capture the most beautiful scenery and be prepared to fall in love with the delicious food made with fresh local ingredients.<br /><br />Take a look at our special offers below. This combined with our summer sale gives you a huge saving of £260 per couple (£130 per person). Book now to get these fantastic savings on your summer holiday!</p>
<p><strong>Hurry, this offer ends on 29 February 2020!<br /></strong>Saving applicable to holidays departing in July and August 2020.</p>
</div>
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><strong>Accommodation Offers </strong></h3>
<div class="g4" style="border-bottom: 1px solid #dedede;">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><br /><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/italy/lake-garda/bardolino/hotel-bologna">3* Hotel Bologna</a><br /><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/italy/lake-garda/bardolino/hotel-bologna">Bardolino</a></h3>
<p style="text-align: left;"><img src="/media/13083146/bologna-hotel-for-web.jpeg" alt="Hotel Bologna" data-udi="umb://media/7e301a9959be42dbb0c9f0113ab8cb93" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">This hotel has a superb location in the centre of Bardolino.<br /><br /><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/italy/lake-garda/bardolino/hotel-bologna"><strong>Find out more &gt;</strong></a></p>
</div>
<div class="g4" style="border-bottom: 1px solid #dedede;">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><br /><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/italy/lake-garda/bardolino/parc-hotel-gritti">4* Parc Hotel Gritti</a><br /><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/italy/lake-garda/bardolino/parc-hotel-gritti">Bardolino</a></h3>
<p style="text-align: left;"><img src="/media/13083147/parc-gritti-for-web.jpg" alt="Parc Hotel Grittit" data-udi="umb://media/55f9b9080a2744389b0a9243fc8e1d1b" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">Just a short stroll from the edge of Lake Garda, maintaining a homely atmosphere.<br /><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/italy/lake-garda/bardolino/parc-hotel-gritti"><strong>Find out more &gt;</strong></a></p>
</div>
<div class="g4" style="border-bottom: 1px solid #dedede;">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><br /><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/italy/lake-garda/desenzano/hotel-villa-rosa">4* Hotel Villa Rosa</a><br /><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/italy/lake-garda/desenzano/hotel-villa-rosa">Desenzano</a></h3>
<p style="text-align: left;"><img src="/media/13083148/hotel-villa-rosa-web.jpg" alt="Hotel Villa Rosa" data-udi="umb://media/1f39384eb6e043d18a09c932ab2ba806" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">An elegant lakefront hotel, in an ideal setting, just a short walk from the centre.<br /><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/italy/lake-garda/desenzano/hotel-villa-rosa"><strong>Find out more &gt;</strong></a></p>
</div>
<div class="g4" style="border-bottom: 1px solid #dedede;">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><br /><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/italy/lake-garda/garda/hotel-palme">2.5* Hotel Palme</a><br /><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/italy/lake-garda/garda/hotel-palme">Garda</a></h3>
<p style="text-align: left;"><img src="/media/13083149/palme-garda-for-web.jpeg" alt="Hotel Palme" data-udi="umb://media/077450ee354a4f67a4717eefa37dc862" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">Incredible value in an enviable location. The town centre is just a six-minute walk away.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/italy/lake-garda/garda/hotel-palme"><strong>Find out more &gt;</strong></a></p>
</div>
<div class="g4" style="border-bottom: 1px solid #dedede;">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><br /><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/italy/lake-garda/limone/hotel-europa">3* Hotel Europa</a><br /><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/italy/lake-garda/limone/hotel-europa">Limone</a></h3>
<p style="text-align: left;"><img src="/media/13083150/europe-limone-for-web.jpeg" alt="Hotel Europa" data-udi="umb://media/22cfb8b3b9c14b28aed42c57e4e6f257" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">This hotel offers panoramic views of Limone’s stunning lakefront.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><br /><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/italy/lake-garda/limone/hotel-europa"><strong>Find out more &gt;</strong></a></p>
</div>
<div class="g4" style="border-bottom: 1px solid #dedede;">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><br /><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/italy/lake-garda/malcesine/hotel-capri">3* Hotel Capri</a><br /><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/italy/lake-garda/malcesine/hotel-capri">Malcesine</a></h3>
<p style="text-align: left;"><img src="/media/13083151/hotel-capri-lake-view-for-web.jpg" alt="Hotel Capri" data-udi="umb://media/e5d9dce8227446d9b0f68f0a0a8ff65c" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">Balanced upon the craggy rocks of Malcesine’s coastline, this lovely hotel is in a prime position.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/italy/lake-garda/limone/hotel-europa"><strong>Find out more &gt;</strong></a></p>
</div>
<div class="g4" style="border-bottom: 1px solid #dedede; text-align: center;">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><br /><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/italy/lake-garda/malcesine/hotel-maximilian">4* Hotel Maximilian</a><br /><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/italy/lake-garda/malcesine/hotel-maximilian">Malcesine</a></h3>
<p style="text-align: left;"><img src="/media/13077429/ii_gar_maximilian_view.jpg" alt="Hotel Maximilian" data-udi="umb://media/988ff35264044fcca1af3dd8b5e74e9b" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">Nestled in the picturesque bay of Val di Sogno and offering exceptional service.</p>
 <br /><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/italy/lake-garda/malcesine/hotel-maximilian"><strong>Find out more &gt;</strong></a></div>
<div class="g4" style="border-bottom: 1px solid #dedede; text-align: center;">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><br /><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/italy/lake-garda/riva/grand-hotel-liberty">4* Hotel Liberty</a><br /><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/italy/lake-garda/riva/grand-hotel-liberty">Riva</a></h3>
<p style="text-align: left;"><img src="/media/13083153/liberty-riva-for-web.jpg" alt="Hotel Liberty" data-udi="umb://media/29c3037e6be44067b6f7876e2dc9ab8e" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">Nestled in stunning landscaped gardens, this former palace has a bright and airy interior.</p>
<br /><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/italy/lake-garda/riva/grand-hotel-liberty"><strong>Find out more &gt;</strong></a></div>
<div class="g4" style="border-bottom: 1px solid #dedede;">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><br /><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/italy/lake-garda/riva/hotel-europa-skypool-panorama">4* Hotel Europa</a><br /><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/italy/lake-garda/riva/hotel-europa-skypool-panorama">Riva</a></h3>
<p style="text-align: left;"><img src="/media/13083154/hotel-europa-pool-riva-for-web.jpg" alt="Hotel Europa" data-udi="umb://media/b17900f6079c427498ec837cb937af81" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">Simple and stylish hotel with unrivaled views of the harbour.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><br /><br /><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/italy/lake-garda/riva/hotel-europa-skypool-panorama"><strong>Find out more &gt;</strong></a></p>
</div>
<div class="g4" style="border-bottom: 1px solid #dedede;">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><br /><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/italy/lake-garda/riva/hotel-sole-relax-panorama">4* Hotel Sole</a><br /><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/italy/lake-garda/riva/hotel-sole-relax-panorama">Riva</a></h3>
<p style="text-align: left;"><img src="/media/13083155/hotel_sole_promenade_-riva-for-web.jpg" alt="Hotel Sole" data-udi="umb://media/b0b5885a7a9b494e89614f44cf8fc0d7" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">Nestled in the heart of Riva's vibrant harbour, offering stylish and comfortable accommodation.<br /><br /><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/italy/lake-garda/riva/hotel-sole-relax-panorama"><strong>Find out more &gt;</strong></a></p>
</div>
<div class="g4" style="border-bottom: 1px solid #dedede;">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><br /><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/italy/lake-garda/sirmione/hotel-olivi-thermae-natural-spa#1" data-anchor="#1">3* Hotel Olivi</a><br /><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/italy/lake-garda/sirmione/hotel-olivi-thermae-natural-spa#1" data-anchor="#1">Sirmione</a></h3>
<p style="text-align: left;"><img src="/media/13083156/hotel-olivi-aerial-for-web.jpg" alt="Hotel Olivi" data-udi="umb://media/2fded820c2a245629ab37b9de91a1b16" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span>Tucked away near the end of the Sirmione peninsula yet just a few moments’ walk from the centre.</span><br /><br /><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/italy/lake-garda/sirmione/hotel-olivi-thermae-natural-spa#1" data-anchor="#1"><strong>Find out more &gt;</strong></a></p>
</div>
<div class="g4" style="border-bottom: 1px solid #dedede;">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><br /><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/italy/folgaria-and-lake-lavarone/grand-hotel-astoria">3.5* Grand Hotel Astoria</a><br /><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/italy/folgaria-and-lake-lavarone/grand-hotel-astoria">Folgaria</a></h3>
<p style="text-align: left;"><img src="/media/13083157/astoria-folgaria-for-web.jpg" alt="Grand Hotel Astoria" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">A homely, comfortable hotel with an atmospheric bar and sporting activities on offer.<br /><br /><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/italy/folgaria-and-lake-lavarone/grand-hotel-astoria"><strong>Find out more &gt;</strong></a></p>
</div>
<div class="g4" style="border-bottom: 1px solid #dedede;"></div>
<div class="g12">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong style="font-size: small;">Terms and Conditions</strong></p>
<ul style="font-size: small;">
<li>Equivalent to £130 off per person</li>
<li>Offer applicable to the above mentioned hotels until 29th February, while stocks last</li>
<li>Ends 29th February 2020</li>
<li>Offer available in July and August 2020</li>
<li>Offer not applicable to other destinations or dates</li>
<li>Prices shown on the website include the discount</li>
<li>All prices, offers and availability are correct at time of publishing, are subject to change and can be withdrawn at any time</li>
<li>Offer based on 7 night holidays unless stated otherwise</li>
<li>When clicking through to book, the prices you see for hotels already have these discounts applied<br /><br /></li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>]]></bodyText>
